{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·006.1", "text_original": "皎皎白駒，食我場苗。縶之維之，以永今朝。所謂伊人，於焉逍遙。", "text_normalized": "皎皎白駒，食我場苗。縶之維之，以永今朝。所謂伊人，於焉逍遙。", "notes": "白駒 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·006.2", "text_original": "皎皎白駒，食我場藿。縶之維之，以永今夕。所謂伊人，於焉嘉客。", "text_normalized": "皎皎白駒，食我場藿。縶之維之，以永今夕。所謂伊人，於焉嘉客。", "notes": "白駒 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·006.3", "text_original": "皎皎白駒，賁然來思。爾公爾侯，逸豫無期。慎爾優游，勉爾遁思。", "text_normalized": "皎皎白駒，賁然來思。爾公爾侯，逸豫無期。慎爾優游，勉爾遁思。", "notes": "白駒 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-006__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·006.4", "text_original": "皎皎白駒，在彼空谷，生芻一束。其人如玉，毋金玉爾音，而有遐心。", "text_normalized": "皎皎白駒，在彼空谷，生芻一束。其人如玉，毋金玉爾音，而有遐心。", "notes": "白駒 Chinese stanza 4."}
